s="mt-4 sm:mt-6 pt-4 sm:pt-6 border-t border-indigo-400/30 dark:border-indigo-600/30"><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-indigo-100 dark:text-indigo-300 font-semibold">💡 Pro Tip: Break big tasks into smaller ones for better progress tracking!</p></div></div></div></div><div><div class="mb-4 sm:mb-6"><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">⭐ Starred Notes</h2><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-300 font-semibold text-xs sm:text-sm hover:underline" href="http://localhost:5173/notes" data-discover="true">View All →</a></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6"><div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/50 transition-all duration-300 p-4 sm:p-6 border-t-4 border-yellow-400 dark:border-yellow-500 hover:-translate-y-1 flex flex-col"><p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 line-clamp-4 sm:line-clamp-5 break-words flex-grow mb-3 sm:mb-4 leading-relaxed">should comeplete react project...
